the serialized port to the ID of the cloned port.\n            if(correspondingNewPort) idMap[serializedPort.id] = correspondingNewPort.getID();\n        });\n    \n        // Return the updated ID SRD.DiagramEngine, model: SRD.DiagramModel, clipboardLinks, idMap, mousePosition: { x: number; y: number }, centerX: number, centerY: number): void {\n        clipboardLinks.forEach(serializedLink => mousePosition: { x: number; y: number }, centerX: number, centerY: number): void {\n        let originalLink = model.getLinks().find(link => link.getID() === serializedLink.id);\n        let  \n\n    async function editLiteral(): Promise<void> {\n        const widget = tracker.currentWidget?.content as XPipePanel;\n\n        if (widget) {\n            const selected_node =
